<p align="center"> </p>
<p align="center">Researchers should also be aware of the <a href="/archives/findaids/fonds/m/mcandrew.htm"><b>Gladys McAndrew fonds</b></a> which relates to missionary work and residential schools undertaken by the Anglican Church in Canada from 1943 to 1954.</p>
